  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Programming Deep Brain Stimulation for the treatment of Essential Tremor can be a time
      intensive process. Using an atlas created using functional tremor responses in the operating
      room to determine the optimal settings would lead to a faster response for the patient and
      improved quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
